{"tid":1806900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民公投］開花與否","createTime":"2020-01-01T14:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T14:52:25.000Z","uid":199670,"like":84,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2148d99bfbe4a9d10871a4a383ddd4fd793e8708","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"經過今日既遊行人數  我肯定我哋嘅士氣返晒黎<br />\n唔會再好似之前咁樣吹雞都得幾十人<br />\n<br />\n但今日之後有咩活動到而家都冇人知<br />\n和你shop/開花/地區遊行應該要快啲再搞<br />\n唔可以降溫   <br />\n<br />\n如果18區每區有一千人以上 我覺得可以開花<br />\n<br />\n重新開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n危險&amp;其他更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之要快啲籌備不停的抗爭活動<br />\n個人覺得而家人夠既話開花仲安全"},{"pid":"022502b1908082d1988d52d4ea93ab24ac468b22","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7102849a3dc3712594ffe45a24da50bb1009e086","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:19:38.000Z","msg":"快啲文宣搞活動  好期待"},{"pid":"52fb0318fb4f48e3bd40e5dd06e31d5408fe1810","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"繼續和你shop既呢到正皮"},{"pid":"2d78babcc9f98c2752fa458ba5d351099fa125da","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35a1a626a9c72eb388fe89811d172c1b2b62ac7a","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩活動"},{"pid":"bd8d0591db192cc917ab000d8d85dcd1d2d7485d","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩做 好悶"},{"pid":"77fae8e67c74e0b4fb8dc2c919342f20118bfffd","tid":1806900,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以話我知"},{"pid":"c8acd4